      "comment": "PAW FAROK (6) quickly into stride to win over the 450m at Ballarat two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to his name from eight starts. Winning claims. PAW VINE (2) shapes well for this backing up a slick 23.24 win with success at this track over 460m last time, recording 26.04. Expecting another bold showing. PAW MAUD (1) filled a minor placing last start at Shepparton behind Zipping Koster (25.69) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expecting another good run. SMOOTH PRINCE (4) is another with top-three prospects.",
